on your brows♪

360
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:19,980
♪Memories entwine reality♪

361
00:15:20,260 --> 00:15:24,340
♪The cycle of stars continues,
only you anchor me♪

362
00:15:24,340 --> 00:15:27,140
♪Through joys and sorrows♪

363
00:15:27,420 --> 00:15:30,820
♪So many obsessions, all in vain♪

364
